Date: Mon, 18 May 2015 11:31:59 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 8/9] i2c/gpio: select i2c_designware and gpio-dwapb

Intel Quark MFD PCI driver for I2C & GPIO requires
gpio-dwapb and i2c_designware as platform driver.
select them to enable MFD driver.

Signed-off-by: Pengyu Ma <pengyu.ma@windriver.com>
---
 drivers/mfd/Kconfig |    2 ++
 1 files changed, 2 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/drivers/mfd/Kconfig b/drivers/mfd/Kconfig
index 083571c..101b97f 100644
--- a/drivers/mfd/Kconfig
+++ b/drivers/mfd/Kconfig
@@ -221,6 +221,8 @@ config MFD_INTEL_QUARK_I2C_GPIO
 	depends on X86
 	depends on COMMON_CLK
 	select MFD_CORE
+	select I2C_DESIGNWARE_PLATFORM
+	select GPIO_DWAPB
 	help
